# Keep the Docker build context small and host-safe. node_modules/target are
# rebuilt inside the container; the Windows TTS + built site never belong there.
# NOTE: src-tauri/icons/*.png ARE needed for the bundle — do not blanket-ignore PNGs.
.git
node_modules
dist
site
linux-dist
src-tauri/target
src-tauri/resources/tts
src-tauri/resources/tts-linux
Screenshot*.png
*.log
scratchpad
